---
title: Our thoughts about web development, startups and entrepreneurship
pageable: true
body_class: blog
---

- page_articles.each do |article|
  %article.preview
    %h2
      = link_to article.title, article
    %p.excerpt= article.summary(100, ' ...')

.pagination
  .prev{:class => prev_page ? "" : "disabled"}
    - if prev_page
      =link_to "← Previous", prev_page.url
    
  .next{:class => next_page ? "" : "disabled"}
    - if next_page
      =link_to "Next →", next_page.url